{
  "stem": "23626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact-- as a matter of fact, only Poldek Pfefferberg, you know, reminded me that sometimes I would run out from the villa and bring sandwiches to the people they would march up to work.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took big chances by helping people with food, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of chances I took, a lot of chances, because I had to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in the position that I had to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we go every year to the cemetery in Long Island, where we have monument with the names of our parents that perished in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every year, we go for Yizkor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Quite a few years ago, my sister was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she says, come, somebody wants to meet you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a gentleman said to me, you know, I want you to meet my wife.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said to his wife, you know, this young girl saved my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, there was so many incidents like this that I don't-- didn't really recall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this special one is because my sister was standing so proud.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, you know, you were down in the office, in Goeth's office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Evidently, I was called to something, to bring something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think it were the keys-- or maybe it were the keys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because I saw two men standing, two prisoners, and Goeth in front of a large glass cabinet, with all medical instruments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Evidently, those were the keys that I brought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because suddenly, he said-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You have-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[DRINKS] He ordered them to move the cabinet to another room, down the hall, down the corridor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he says, but if anything breaks, you will die.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
